    <string name="onboarding_welcome_title">Welcome to VOD</string>
    <string name="onboarding_welcome_desc">This quick guide will show you how to navigate and use the app. Use the Next button or swipe to continue.</string>
    
    <string name="onboarding_navigation_title">How to Navigate</string>
    <string name="onboarding_navigation_desc">Use your D-pad or remote to navigate. The side menu on the left has Search, Home, Watch Later, and your content libraries. Navigate up/down to move between menu items, then press right or OK to enter each section.</string>
    
    <string name="onboarding_browsing_title">Browsing Content</string>
    <string name="onboarding_browsing_desc">The Home screen shows a featured title at the top. Navigate down to browse Continue Watching and content rows. Select any title to view details, or press Play to start watching immediately.</string>
    
    <string name="onboarding_profiles_title">Using Profiles</string>
    <string name="onboarding_profiles_desc">Each family member can have their own profile with separate watch history. Select your profile at the bottom of the side menu to switch profiles. Long-press it to open Playback Preferences. In the profile picker, long-press a profile to set it as default for auto-login.</string>
    
    <string name="onboarding_search_title">Search &amp; Filters</string>
    <string name="onboarding_search_desc">Select Search from the side menu to find content. Type your query, then use the filter chips below to narrow results by Movies, Series, or genre (Action, Comedy, Drama, etc.). Select Clear to reset filters.</string>
    
    <string name="onboarding_watchlist_title">Watch Later &amp; Progress</string>
    <string name="onboarding_watchlist_desc">On any title, select the Watch Later button to save it for later. Your watchlist and viewing progress sync across devices. Continue Watching on the Home screen shows titles you haven\'t finished.</string>
    
    <string name="onboarding_playback_title">Playback Controls</string>
    <string name="onboarding_playback_desc">During playback: use left/right to seek, OK to pause/play, and back to exit. For series, a Next Episode button appears at the end. Resume will pick up where you left off, or choose Play to start from the beginning.</string>

    <string name="onboarding_pinning_title">Pin Your Favourites</string>
    <string name="onboarding_pinning_desc">Long-press any library in the side menu to pin it to the top of the list for quick access. Long-press again to unpin. Your pinned libraries are saved per profile.</string>

